{"tid":138511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Steve Jobs遺作】全球最節能建築，蘋果基地「Apple Park」四月啟用","createTime":"2017-02-28T15:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T04:23:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d87b3878ebf1219a9d5aa5109a2191655e893d80","tid":138511,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Screen-Shot-2017-02-23-at-4.58.59-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FScreen-Shot-2017-02-23-at-4.58.59-PM.png&h=14a49ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司正式宣佈，將位於美國矽谷的新總部命名為「Apple Park」，由四月開始陸續安排員工遷入，亦會開放予公眾參觀。蘋果表示，Apple Park是全球最節能的建築之一，皆因建築樓頂裝滿了太陽能電板，未來將會完全依靠可再生能源運作。當中大部份的設計構想均由已故蘋果創辦人Steve Jobs提出，故亦被外界視為「Steve Jobs的遺作」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Apple<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司昨天宣佈，將一直以「Apple Campus 2」為代號的新總部，正式命名為Apple Park，由四月開始陸續安排舊總部超過12,000名員工遷入，預計耗時大約半年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Apple<br />\n<br />\nApple Park主大樓佔地280萬平方英尺， 外型酷似環狀太空艦，以號稱是全球最大的曲面玻璃包圍着。建築樓頂裝滿了太陽能電板，可供應17兆瓦電力，以達到百分百使用可再生能源運作為目標。Apple Park亦是全球最大的自然通風建築之一，預計一年當中有七成的時間無須開啟冷暖空調，達到最佳的節能效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Apple<br />\n<br />\nApple Park大部份的設計構想均由已故蘋果創辦人Steve Jobs提出，故亦被外界視為「Steve Jobs的遺作」。為紀念Steve Jobs，新基地大會堂被命名為「Steve Jobs Theatre」。今年蘋果的新機發佈會，極有可能會在這個可容納上千人的大會堂內舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by Digital Trends<br />\n<br />\n蘋果CEO Tim Cook表示，「Steve Jobs希望Apple Park成為未來的創新基地。新總部不但激發蘋果團隊繼續向前邁進，同時亦為地球環境出一分力。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/02/23/article/21461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2Farticle%2F21461%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0e139444\" target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/02/23/article/21461/</a>"},{"pid":"a7a51e71c846b1d50e6b7bc231132c1e3c9f2941","tid":138511,"uid":79205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:13:43.000Z","msg":"我諗遲啲強國都會有個一模一樣"},{"pid":"556ff2cdefb5de7c3b6dce81cee654a1529edb81","tid":138511,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:30:57.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287390e344ec1aa1be01fb45ccae444d1cab9184","tid":138511,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:36:07.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4423759c29681a42ccf9ab5853bdc5126dca8b0d","tid":138511,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T21:30:19.000Z","msg":"Tim cook:又係時候穢土轉生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6587a83055df278e944801b85458c980096ed1f1","tid":138511,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T22:31:23.000Z","msg":"轉行做地產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556772dc987e9cf6f3cb9d9267fb540356bb80c6","tid":138511,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"成個 home button 咁"},{"pid":"5d838cb9c24e5a8687d761f88cd3c6dc4f140704","tid":138511,"uid":79138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"遲d小米又整返個米park<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e5d7bf9cb21a0e652848819bbf07ec3605ec7d","tid":138511,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲d小米又整返個米park<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n米你老母"},{"pid":"2c985c766ea2fc8fbf857906182eca7e737db99f","tid":138511,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:08:31.000Z","msg"